{"tid":1264282,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"知己知彼 中共分化香港人技倆盤點","createTime":"2019-06-28T15:27:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T14:18:51.000Z","uid":123713,"like":50,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2f029facaf87c5579933c9bf7353950641def29d","tid":1264282,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T15:27:56.000Z","msg":"中共最近真係出盡奶力想搞分化同離間<br />\n間接證明大家既所有付出係威脅緊中共<br />\n<br />\n不過中共係搞分化 情報 輿論戰有咁撚多年經驗<br />\n真係好撚恐怖<br />\n<br />\n不過唔撚驚 一齊集思廣益<br />\n見招拆招！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1. LIHKG PARTY扮籌款再插贓嫁禍<br />\n上次眾籌登報後<br />\n而家有條個建制狗假<br />\n借LIHKG PARTY名義開始眾籌300萬<br />\n極有可能建制科水籌夠三百萬<br />\n再扮晒野食夾棍<br />\n屈尻連登仔籌錢騙局<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1263521\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1263521</a><br />\n<br />\n2. Google search ads<br />\n而家係google search &ldquo;free Hong Kong&rdquo; &ldquo; Hong Kong&rdquo; &ldquo;遊行等字眼<br />\n會彈出一個建制網控訴反送中擾亂香港既網<br />\n入面仲有幾經辛苦先剪到出黎既&rdquo;暴徒L&rdquo;片<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1262613\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1262613</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3. 搵人扮判頭請人遊行/衝擊<br />\n4. 警犬混入集會群眾 意圖煽動衝擊<br />\n5. 係警總叫白車但又唔柒開門<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n集氣！"},{"pid":"1723bcd7fd31f04ab79c63688ed4d655705a9881","tid":1264282,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T15:29:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9ce6ec9dbcfe446ba9a119043cce45cd52466ce0","tid":1264282,"uid":234679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T15:30:22.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b6aa68b80a937a36e7cb5d9fd8ef3181d48cb6a6","tid":1264282,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T15:30:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1e9ffbfabfa982cdf91e6fdbe54c9471ad3aca17","tid":1264282,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T15:31:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"98ca451e5c66c6ef1225670b9c84f9f625074edf","tid":1264282,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T15:35:45.000Z","msg":